Class AccountTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • AccountTest

  • public class AccountTest
extends java.lang.Object
    JUnit test class for the Account class. Tests core account operations, such as deposit, withdrawal, balance retrieval, and transfer functionality in a Checking account.
